ntainer\" class=\"container\"><div class=\"van_headline star\"><h1>Casting</h1></div><div class=\"post\"><div class=\"entry\"><div class=\"wpb_row vc_row-fluid parallax\"><div class=\"vc_span12 wpb_column column_container\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_el_width_100 vc_sep_color_grey\"> <span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l\"><span class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span><h4>Why Cristina\u00b4S Secrets ?</h4> <span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r\"><span class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11599\" src=\"http://cristinassecrets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/castinf.jpg\" alt=\"castinf\" width=\"1767\" height=\"500\" /></p></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p>* Because we are an agency with an excellent international reputation .</p><p>* Because we are an agency with over 23 years of existence.</p><p>* Because we plan your appointments with confidence.</p><p>* Because we have a large customer base.</p><p>* Because we respect your conditions.</p><p>* Because we protect the privacy and do not teach your data , pictures etc.</p><p><strong>OUR REQUIREMENTS.</strong></p><p>If you are between \u00a018 to 30 years, physically attractive, with a friendly and warm personality, you are educated and able to hold an intelligent conversation.- Maintain a healthy lifestyle .</p><p><strong>It is required-</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-No drugs .</p><p>-Spanish or European nationality</p><p>&#8211; Be discreet in the way they dress .</p><p>&#8211; Do not focus exclusively on being escort.</p><p>&#8211; send at least 2 photos required (face and body, natural and without any retouching since these photos are just to see your profile and not to publish on our website)</p><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">- No photos are allowed with clogged or blur face.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">- (no request will be answered without these requirements)</span></p><p>&#8211; In our agency never any model without knowing previously published.</p><p>&#8211; If all is well I&#8217;ll call you to arrange a personal interview.</p><p>And finally, if we agree , I expect a very good collaboration.</p><p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">*</span> The agency takes charge managing the photographic book, without any cost for your part.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong> \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 OUR AGENCY NEVER PROVIDES PHOTOS OF LADIES OPEN FACE</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-top: 28px;\"><strong><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-7530 size-full\" src=\"http://cristinassecrets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Unknown-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" /><a href=\"tel:+34639254544\">\u00a0\u00a0<span style=\"color: #000000;\">+ 34 639 25 45 44</span></a></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-top: 28px;\"><strong>\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-7549 size-full\" src=\"http://cristinassecrets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/whassap.jpg\" alt=\"whassap\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" />WhatsApp :<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"tel:+34639254544\">+ 34 639254544</a></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-top: 28px;\"><strong><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-7531 size-full\" src=\"http://cristinassecrets.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Unknown.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"mailto:cristina@madamecristina.com\">cristina@madamecristina.com</a></span><br /> </strong></p></div></div><div class=\"vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_el_width_100 vc_sep_color_grey\"> <span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l\"><span class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span> <span class=\"vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r\"><span class=\"vc_sep_line\"></span></span></div><